title: Burn Notice (2007) Season One
description:
Plot: A spy recently disavowed by the US Government uses his Special Ops training to help others in trouble. 

Excellent show. The show is well acted and the stories are good. I've enjoyed the show since the beginning.

This torrent contains all 12 episodes of the first season. Episodes 11 & 12 are one file.
